text: Cazenovia College was a private college in Cazenovia, New York. It had 800 students in Fall 2020. It closed in 2023. Cazenovia College started in 1824 with the name Genesee Seminary. It was called Cazenovia Seminary from 1894 to 1982. == References == == Other websites == * * Official athletics website * The Bonnie Monroe Fashion Illustration Collection from Cazenovia College on New York Heritage Digital Collections Category:1824 establishments in the United States Category:2023 disestablishments in the United States Category:Colleges and universities in New York (state)
